    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Apparatuses for making coffee by forcing boiled water under pressure through finely ground coffee. They are used primarily for making espresso and other traditional Italian coffee-based beverages.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000093795/Encyclopedia Britannica Online (2002-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000114707/Oxford English Dictionary Online (2002-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Apparat zur Herstellung von Kaffee, indem kochendes Wasser unter Druck durch fein gemahlenes Kaffeepulver gedrückt wird. Es wird hauptsächlich zur Zubereitung von Espresso und anderen traditionell italienischen, auf Kaffee basierenden Getränken verwendet.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>German</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000232/IfM-SMB-PK</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000122134/IfM Berlin</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Apparaten waarmee men koffie kan maken door kokend water onder druk door fijngemalen koffie te leiden. Men gebruikt ze primair om espresso te maken en andere traditionele Italiaanse koffiedranken.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>利用高壓迫使滾水迅速通過細磨咖啡粉的咖啡裝置，主要用來煮濃縮咖啡和其他以咖啡為基底的傳統義式飲料。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
